            "question": {
                "text": "Let X be the number of distinct 16-bit integers in 2's \ncomplement representation. Let Y be the number of \ndistinct \n16-bit \nintegers \nin \nsign \nmagnitude \nrepresentation. Then X-Y is _________.",
