                "1"
            ],
            "solution": {
                "text": "If x is in 2's then range of x will be  \n\n-2n-1 to 2n-1 -1 \n\nHere x is 16 bits number, n = 16  \n\n-216-1 to 216-1 -1 \n\nx = 65536 \n\nIf y is in sign magnitude representation, then range \nof y will be \n\n- (2n-1-1) to + (2n-1 -1) \nn = 16 \n\n- (216-1-1) to + (216-1 -1) \n\ny = 65535  \n\nHence, x - y = 1",
                "images": [],
